title: Batman & Robin host the ABC 1966 fall preview line-up
description:
This originally aired in 1966.  In older times, networks would make a TV special showing off their new TV shows for the upcoming Fall new season.

This  is a VHS Rip of ABC&#039;s fall preview for the 1966-67 TV season.

What makes this show so special is that it was Hosted by Batman (Adam West) and Robin (B urt Ward) along with special guest Milton Berle.  This program is commercial free and runs for about 40 minutes.  The New TV shows for the time period that this special highlights to the "new" shows are:

IRON HORSE
RAT PATROL
THE ROUNDERS (starring John Wayne&#039;s son)
THE PRUITT&#039;S OF SOUTH HAMPTON (Phylis Diller)
LOVE ON A ROOFTOP
WILD COUNTRY
THE MAN WHO NEVER WAS
THE TAMMY GRIMES SHOW
THAT GIRL (Marlo Thomas)
HAWK (Burt Reynolds first show)
GREEN HORNET (Bruce Lee)
TIME TUNNEL
SHANE (David Carridine)

as well as mentioning many more shows returning for another season

You will NOT find this show anywhere but here!  This is a rarity and is posted first on PIRATE BAY!

THIS IS NOT ON DEMONOID!  Because I don&#039;t have an account there.  (hint hint)
